data.text:
2015

Documentary, Comedy

Watchlist

Welsh comedian, actor and presenter Rob Brydon retraces his rocky road to success, from his early days in Porthcawl to Hollywood. Featuring a host of famous friends that joined Rob on his journey including Sir Tom Jones, Steve Coogan, Ruth Jones and David Walliams.
